    "body": "approve(address _spender, uint256 _value) function of Simple Token will allow _spender to transfer tokens from **msg.sender** account.\r\n\r\nWhen tokenApprove(AddTokenContractAddress,1000) calls approve() function, msg.sender gets changed to address of addToken contract. That means you are allowing AddTokenContractAddress to transfer token from AddTokenContractAddress itself.\r\n\r\nYou can verify that by calling tokenAllowance(AddTokenContractAddress,AddTokenContractAddress) \r\n\r\nSo, there is nothing wrong with approve() function.",
